{"tid":1390653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城Online] 突發遊擊兵裝備","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:37:26.000Z","uid":90735,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f294ac02156cf187af9d062dd19fe489b0d623c","tid":1390653,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>以下係全城最熱門線上遊戲「香港Online」討論</strong><br />\n由於突發遊擊兵係支援突發事件，所以返工返學時，袋入面一定要長期擺幾樣遊戲道具：<br />\n<br />\n帽<br />\n黑超<br />\n面巾／口罩<br />\n黑衫<br />\n兩條索帶<br />\n背囊防雨罩<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下遊戲道具可於補給點即場課金購買</strong><br />\n遮，自衛用<br />\n樽裝飲品<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>心法：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攻其不備<br />\nBe Water：如浪濤拍岸，如急流湧退</span></span>"},{"pid":"c174c9f11f0af68e8f14916090e2837650ff6139","tid":1390653,"uid":198932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minutemen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMinutemen&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=01eaa2d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minutemen</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4b/Minute_Man_Statue_Lexington_Massachusetts_cropped.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F4b%2FMinute_Man_Statue_Lexington_Massachusetts_cropped.jpg&h=6516c6d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"481161fb6db0aebbb450f8cae2ed0e2be81bfe76","tid":1390653,"uid":90735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c174c9f11f0af68e8f14916090e2837650ff6139","tid":1390653,"uid":198932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minutemen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMi